{"tid":725820,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男子毀14支支國旗區旗　途人阻止遭止汗劑噴面","createTime":"2018-07-02T02:23:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-02T22:00:07.000Z","uid":51271,"like":113,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"2b77f33acf8153d3251e03edb7bd0846c9c80356","tid":725820,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T02:23:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180702/s00001/1530496886827\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180702%2Fs00001%2F1530496886827&d=fyCun59eG1Q4uXOCRK3Ijm6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=f68ada20\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180702%2Fs00001%2F1530496886827&h=a6f58447\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180702/s00001/1530496886827</a><br />\n<br />\n深水埗石硤尾邨一服務設施大樓外，昨晚10時許，一名33歲姓盧男子連環掃低插在路邊欄杆的國旗及區旗，一名60歲姓梁路人途經上址嘗試阻止，惟遭盧用手及止汗劑襲擊。途人報警，警方到場發現有14枝國旗及區旗損毀，警方經初步調查，將盧以涉嫌刑事毀壞及普通襲擊拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n案件交由深水埗警區刑事調查隊第八隊跟進。梁姓路人則報稱面部、眼晴及腹部受傷，被送到明愛醫院治理。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180702/s00001/771b7d32b4e5daefe6d62151c0fcc3dc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180702%2Fs00001%2F771b7d32b4e5daefe6d62151c0fcc3dc.jpg&h=b0ad0240&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180702/s00001/771ea7639a674363e884ac3676762cef.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180702%2Fs00001%2F771ea7639a674363e884ac3676762cef.jpg&h=b3548a47&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b58b08adcb9be880834f60eddff5aebbb6d8c041","tid":725820,"uid":37528,"like":135,"dislike":4,"score":131,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T02:24:47.000Z","msg":"一名60歲姓梁路人途經上址嘗試阻止<br />\n<br />\n多鳩事廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}